      "span_text": "Although the allosteric mTORC1 inhibitor rapamycin did not block the polarization of M2 macrophages ( Supplementary Fig. 6 ), the ATP-competitive mTOR inhibitor Torin1 (ref. ) blocked the expression of M2 signature genes Arg1, IL10 and RELMa in dose-dependent manner (Fig. 3f)."
